## Instructions
Analyze the match across these dimensions:
1. Skills match (list matched, missing, and extra skills)
2. Experience match (years and relevance)
3. Education match (degree and field alignment)
4. Location match (remote compatibility, geographic proximity)
5. Title match (role seniority alignment)

Return JSON:
- overall_score: integer 0-100
- skills_score: integer 0-100
- experience_score: integer 0-100
